nodes.title: RES4LYF Nodes
widgets_values:
### This workflow uses RES4LYF nodes. 
These nodes are capable of producing higher quality and more detailed videos at the expense of generation time. 

For faster generations, use the alternative T2V/I2V workflows

nodes.title: Steps Guide
widgets_values:
## High noise steps should be generally lower than half of the total steps for crisp detail. 

For example, for 24 steps I would use 9 high noise steps
